      "question": "players on the 10-day,15-day or 60-Day injured list on the San Francisco Giants in 2020-2021",
      "sql": "SELECT TOP (100)  r.person__full_name, t.name AS team_name,\n       r.position__name, r.status__description, r.season\nFROM dw.rosters r\nJOIN dw.teams t ON t.id = r.parent_team_id\nWHERE r.season BETWEEN 2020 AND 2021\nAND r.status__description IN ('Injured 10-Day', 'Injured 15-Day', 'Injured 60-Day')\nAND t.name = 'San Francisco Giants'\nORDER BY r.season DESC, r.status__description, r.person__full_name",
